{"tid":2508776,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登承諾會確保中國遵守國際規則","createTime":"2021-04-29T04:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T04:24:14.000Z","uid":278587,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3965d30c23d19a32b928be9a1276b9c0da08c0f0","tid":2508776,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:11:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=432882\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D432882&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzQEOIADdcgve6BSnlMLQ7pQ%3D&h=ab679153\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D432882&h=f83ce7a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=432882</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】即將就職滿一百日的美國總統拜登首次到國會發表演說，他提到中國，承諾會確保中國遵守國際規則。<br />\n<br />\n拜登：「我今晚提出的投資，亦會促進惠及中產的外交政策，即是確保所有國家在全球經濟框架下跟從相同規則，包括中國。」<br />\n<br />\n「我跟中國國家主席習近平溝通時，我告訴他，我們歡迎競爭，並不尋求衝突，但同時絕對清晰表明會捍衛美國各方面的利益。美國會對抗削弱美國工人及工業的不公平貿易行為，像國家對企業的補貼及竊取美國技術和知識產權。」"},{"pid":"bd24daa7c0040e2eb3a097f703400ebbd3288351","tid":2508776,"uid":63909,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:17:34.000Z","msg":"行撚開啦<br />\n美國行政區書記<br />\n你點可能做到呀<br />\n扮到幾時"},{"pid":"31b10fd0601757123b5a73518a2075fccd4d2612","tid":2508776,"uid":22701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:23:25.000Z","msg":"點解係由國家A去承諾國家B會守規則？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b99afc2168e594c1d6597ad2f3aa3c8e7c1195","tid":2508776,"uid":22590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:24:14.000Z","msg":"話可以確保中國遵守乜乜, 仲唔係赤裸裸既霸權主義<br />\n煽動全球輿論，幻想達到&ldquo;不戰而屈人之兵&rdquo;的效果<br />\n達成其美國優先、維持霸權的目的<br />\n直接干預他國內政、歪曲事實、煽動仇恨"}]}